OL,3,CFour charged after violent disorder
OL,4,Cagainst police in Liverpool
OL,6,FPolice have charged four men with
OL,7,Fviolent disorder after riots broke out
OL,8,Fin Liverpool city centre in the wake
OL,9,Fof the Southport stabbings.
OL,11,FJimmy Bailey, 45, of Station Avenue,
OL,12,FEllesmere Port, was charged after a
OL,13,Fgroup was seen throwing stones, bricks
OL,14,Fand missiles at police on Saturday 3
OL,15,FAugust.
OL,17,FA row of officers moved to take one of
OL,18,Fthe suspects to the ground and detain
OL,19,Fhim, Merseyside Police said.
