OL,3,CFour charged after violent disorder
OL,4,Cagainst police in Liverpool
OL,6,FLloyd Killner, 35, of Burton Road,
OL,7,FLincoln, has also been charged with
OL,8,Fviolent disorder after a group was
OL,9,Fseen in Stanley Street charging and
OL,10,Fswearing at officers, and throwing
OL,11,Fmissiles.
OL,13,FLiam James Riley, 41, of Walton Road,
OL,14,FKirkdale was charged with violent
OL,15,Fdisorder.
OL,17,FAll four have been remanded in custody
OL,18,Fto appear at Liverpool Magistrates'
OL,19,FCourt on Monday.
