OL,3,CFour charged after violent disorder
OL,4,Cagainst police in Liverpool
OL,6,FFollowing the scenes in Liverpool
OL,7,FMerseyside Police has introduced two
OL,8,Fsection 60 orders giving officers
OL,9,Fgreater stop-and-search powers
OL,10,Fcovering the city and Southport.
OL,12,FThe orders were put in place at 2pm on
OL,13,FSunday and will stay active for a 12-
OL,14,Fhour period until 2am on Monday.
OL,16,FThe orders cover areas across
OL,17,FLiverpool and Southport and are
OL,18,Fdesigned to prevent serious violence.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/6
