OL,3,CFour charged after violent disorder
OL,4,Cagainst police in Liverpool
OL,6,FInspector Al McKeon said: "The scenes
OL,7,Fwe saw yesterday in Liverpool and
OL,8,FWalton, and on Tuesday in Southport,
OL,9,Fwere despicable.
OL,11,F"They left dozens of officers
OL,12,Frequiring hospital treatment and have
OL,13,Falready led to the arrests of a total
OL,14,Fof 33 suspects.
