OL,6,F"These orders will give officers on
OL,7,Fthe ground the ability to stop and
OL,8,Fsearch anyone suspected of carrying
OL,9,Fweapons or planning any criminality.
OL,10,FThe ultimate aim of this tool is to
OL,11,Fprevent violence and disorder and keep
OL,12,Fthe public safe.
OL,14,F"People across the areas covered will
OL,15,Fsee targeted and highly visible police
OL,16,Fpatrols over the next 12 hours. I hope
OL,17,Ftheir continued presence is reassuring
OL,18,Ffor all of our communities, and I
OL,19,Fwould ask anyone with concerns to
OL,20,Fspeak to those officers."
